**Fix:**  
```javascript
function register(trigger, panel) {
  // …existing code…
  setAttr(trigger, 'aria-controls', panelId);
  // Initialise state
  setAttr(trigger, 'aria-expanded', 'false');   // ← add this
  // …rest of function…
}
```
and in `_openInstance`/`_closeInstance` toggle the attribute:
```javascript
function _openInstance(inst) {
  // …existing code…
  setAttr(inst.trigger, 'aria-expanded', 'true');   // ← add
}
function _closeInstance(inst) {
  // …existing code…
  setAttr(inst.trigger, 'aria-expanded', 'false'); // ← add
}
```

